\F[24]\AA[F](Despite being a stuffed animal, it was stubborn and
kept running away. I'm glad I drained the strong Hayato-kun.)
\F[18]\AA[F]Why did you do such a thing!!

\F[24]\AA[F]\c[14]I was talking about the weapon\c[0], wasn't I. You
see, if that gets known, Lady Sadi will be in trouble.

\F[39]\AA[F]There was no need to make a mess of the place where
Ann was!

\F[39]\AA[F]Monsters are always like this! They take away lives
and places like this!!
\F[24]\AA[F]What? Rather, he went too far on his own.

\F[24]\AA[F]He even moved things unnecessarily under the guise of
operation, and even spilled classified information....
\F[20]\AA[F]You were also targeted, weren't you? Isn't that good.
................... \c[14]I want you to listen to my troubles\c[0].

Aren't you going to laugh? 'A spirit without a physical form
falling in love' and all that...

No matter who the other person is, I will definitely... not laugh
at you.

\F[24]\AA[F](Dirty work is also too much.... I wonder if I should
get comforted by Hayato-kun.)

\F[40]\AA[F]In the rules... \c[14]there wasn't any mention that
Seria can't kill Merill\c[0], was there?

\F[40]\AA[F]\{You thought I was a woman who couldn't do anything
and looked down on me, didn't you?

\F[24]\AA[F](This is... \c[14]the power of a goddess...? \c[0] It's
nothing like I imagined...!)

\F[40]\AA[F]If I really try, I can do this much.... \{I can do
it!!!

Ann is a spirit! Even if her vessel doll is destroyed, she won't
die!
You must not let your anger over Ann consume you!
\F[24]\AA[F]Ah... I'm all sweaty because of your flames.
I wonder if I should have Hayato-kun lick it off...♡
My breasts, armpits, butt, thighs... everything...♡
There's no way he would do something so disgusting, right?!

Who knows? The Hayato-kun I know seems like he would do it
though♡
\F[17]\AA[F](My strength is draining... My consciousness is...)
\F[17]\AA[F]Was I... laid down on the bed?

\F[10]\AA[F]You were about to say something... Could it be
Anthurium?

While you were unconscious, I manipulated your body to... the
bed.
\F[10]\AA[F]My body doesn't hurt, but I feel strangely tired....

\F[1]\AA[F]I remember Anthurium's voice, but the rest is a
blur...
Isn't this place a total mess!
You don't have to force yourself to remember.
\c[14]You got angry for Anthurium's sake\c[0]. That alone is enough.

\F[17]\AA[F](.....Did I lose my temper and faint? I'm such a
mess....)
Hehehe. That's not the case, Miss Seria.

\F[10]\AA[F]I'd like to sew you up if I could, but I'm really bad
at sewing....

\F[1]\AA[F]Speaking of which, a few months ago... I received a
stuffed animal from Hayato.

\F[10]\AA[F]I've completely turned it into a hug pillow. I hugged
it so tightly that the cotton came out....
\F[1]\AA[F]Hey, why is this child left here?
\F[18]\AA[F]This, you see, is the source of the pleasant scent!

\F[6]\AA[F]I remember winning a prize at a piano competition when
I was living in the city.
It seems to burst, you know.

\F[1]\AA[F].........Ah. There seems to be a piece of paper stuck
here. Is this it?

I want to passionately embrace Lady Sadi. But, I'm a spirit that
can't take form unless I possess something.

It's frustrating, it's frustrating, it's frustrating, it's
frustrating, it's frustrating, it's frustrating. It's
frustrating, it's frustrating, it's frustrating, it's
frustrating, it's frustrating, it's frustrating.
